⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Deterrence Broadcast & the Photoid
node 3BT · 3BT · ⟦Deterrence Broadcast & the Photoid:3BT:430001⟧

WHO   — Deterrence Broadcast & the Photoid — gravitational-wave antennas that hold a world hostage — and the star-killing bullet
WHAT  — Dark-forest deterrence is enforced by gravitational-wave transmitters that can broadcast Trisolaris's coordinates to the silent hunters. The proof that the dark forest is real: a 'photoid,' a near-lightspeed kinetic projectile, is used to destroy a star (187J3X1).
WHERE — 3BT · The Technologia of Trisolaris  Framework inputs: Remembrance of Earth's Past + adaptations; real-science verdict  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Both are book-two/three concepts; not reached by the live-action series.
HOW   — HALF. Gravitational waves are completely real — LIGO detected them in 2015 (Nobel 2017). But using them as a galaxy-wide, directional communications beacon is fiction: they are absurdly hard to generate or detect at any usable signal level. The photoid (a light-speed star-killing bullet) is FLUFF.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Gravitational waves are real; using them to whisper your enemy's address to the hunters is not.

